11. Signs announcing ales, provided that such signs:
a. Do not exceed one sign per site of the sale;
b. Do not exceed four square feet in area per display surface; and
C. Are removed within seven days of posting.
12. Announcements by public or nonprofit organizations of special events or activities of interest to the general
